To make the breadcrumbs: To make the breadcrumbs: Preheat the oven to 300°. Cut the bread (including crusts) into 2-inch chunks and put the chunks on a baking tray. Bake for about 10 minutes, until the bread is thoroughly dried out. 3. Let the bread cool slightly–just enough to handle. Pulse the bread in a food processor until it is reduced to coarse crumbs. To make the crumbs Yo!: To make the crumbs Yo!: